Package org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3

Interface NucleicAcidReference

All Superinterfaces:
BioPAXElement, Cloneable, EntityReference, Level3Element, Named, Observable, SequenceEntityReference, Serializable, UtilityClass, XReferrable
All Known Subinterfaces:
DnaReference, DnaRegionReference, NucleicAcidRegionReference, RnaReference, RnaRegionReference
All Known Implementing Classes:
DnaReferenceImpl, DnaRegionReferenceImpl, NucleicAcidReferenceImpl, NucleicAcidRegionReferenceImpl, RnaReferenceImpl, RnaRegionReferenceImpl
public interface NucleicAcidReference extends SequenceEntityReference
Role interface for NucleicAcidReferences, namely DNA and RNA. They share the common behaviour of having "regions" on them.
